antic basin gas markets that will drive the development of future lng trade considering the potential role of brazil in the future market for lng downloads pdf+ agenda modified july 2006 pdf english_program pdf 101.0 kb pdf+ presentation modified august 2006 pdf bertero_south_american_market pdf 1.0 mb pdf+ presentation modified august 2006 pdf brown_northamericanatgas pdf 390.1 kb pdf+ paper modified august 2006 pdf hayes_lng_arbitrage pdf 315.1 kb pdf+ paper modified august 2006 pdf hayes_seasonal_lng_trade pdf 358.8 kb pdf+ presentation modified august 2006 pdf holz_european_gas_market pdf 686.7 kb pdf+ presentation modified august 2006 pdf victor_hayes_convergence pdf 526.3 kb location rio de janeiro brazil fsi contact mark h hayes parent research projects natural gas markets topics natural gas oil brazil europe united states search events everything event news pesd participates in seminar on atlantic basin natural gas markets august 16 2006 news events of interest natural gas in the energy futures of china and india conference pdf+ workshop on natural gas markets in beijing shanghai and guangdong workshop pdf+ support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 724 1714 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
